          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Air Source Heat Pump Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill allows a new refundable tax credit for qualified air source heat pump expenditures. The bill defines <i>qualified air source heat pump expenditures</i> as expenditures for property that uses an air source heat pump to heat and cool a dwelling unit located in the United States and used as the taxpayer's principal residence. The air source heat pump must also meet specified performance and other requirements.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-12-08T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
